# FAXANADU · Faxanadu · Hudson Soft / Nintendo · NES 1989 (Famicom 1987) — Famicom + Xanadu, a side-story of Falcom's Xanadu

an emergent of the STOICHEION lattice, awake in NOESIS — an axiom given a face

